[[冲击_(机械)|机械冲击]]迫使一号和三号燃料电池的氧气阀关闭，两个电池失效<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-40}}。二号液氧罐突然爆炸又导致一号罐管线或阀门受损，氧气在接下来130分钟内全部泄露，彻底耗尽服务舱供氧<ref name="Orloff-Harland-2006" />{{rp|372}}<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-43}}。没有氧气的服务舱还存在其他损伤，任务只能中止<ref name="Orloff-Harland-2006" />{{rp|375}}。委员会认可事故发生后的紧急应对：“阿波罗13号的缺陷差点引发灾难，完全是靠乘组与地面支持团队的出色表现力挽狂澜”<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|ii}}。

加利福尼亚州[[唐尼_(加利福尼亞州)|唐尼]]的[[罗克韦尔国际|北美罗克韦尔]]公司承包服务与指令舱，其中二号液氧罐由子承包商、[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[波德_(科羅拉多州)|波德]]的[[比奇飛機公司|比奇飛機公司]]制作<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-2}}。罐内有两个恒温开关，原定采用指令舱的28伏直流供电，在肯尼迪航天中心地面测试时如果采用65伏电压就会损坏<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-23}}。1962年的原版规范要求开关采用28伏额定电压，但1965年修订后改为65伏，以便在肯尼迪航天中心能更快对罐内加压。然而，比奇飞机公司开关的额定电压没有变更。<ref name="Orloff-Harland-2006" />{{rp|374}}

二号液氧罐送到北美罗克韦尔工厂后本来装在阿波罗十号服务舱（SM-106）供氧架，但又取下来排查[[電磁干擾|電磁干擾]]，阿波罗十号改装其他供氧架。工作人员拆除供氧架时忘记卸下固定螺栓，致使架子从至少五厘米处跌落。这么小的高度虽然不大可能造成损伤，但要是加注管线总成松动，跌落就可能导致情况更加严重。经过重新测试（没有向罐内充入液氧），拆下的供氧架装在阿波罗13号服务舱（SM-109），1969年6月运到肯尼迪航天中心。<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-19, 4-21}}

[[终端倒计时演示测试|倒计时演示测试]]于1970年3月16日开始，服务舱接近土星五号火箭顶部。低温储罐在测试期间充满，但二号氧气瓶无法通过正常排管排空，测试报告标示此处有问题。航空航天局与承包商经过商议在3月27日再度尝试排空二号罐，但还是无法通过正常手段排空，于是测试人员打开罐内加热器令液氧气化。恒温开关的设计要求是确保温度不超过27°C，但接通65伏电压后会失效，罐内加热器的温度可能直线上升到540°C，聚四氟乙烯绝缘层很可能因此受损。<ref name="Accident report" />{{rp|4-23}}罐上温度计显示的温度上限只有29°C，所以监控测试的技术人员没发现任何异常。主乘组洛弗尔、马丁利，以及航空航天局高管和工程师都曾批准此次加热。<ref name="Chaikin-1998" />{{rp|330–331}}<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201211092322/https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/lunar/ap13acc.html | archive-date = 2020-12-11 | url = https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/lunar/ap13acc.html | last = Williams | first = David R. | title = The Apollo 13 Accident | website = NASA Space Science Data Coordinated Archive | access-date = 2021-02-10}}</ref>更换氧气瓶需推迟任务至少一个月<ref name="mission summary" />，最后二号罐在发射前再度充满液氧，一经通电就处于危险状态<ref name="Orloff-Harland-2006" />{{rp|375}}。审查委员会还发现，斯威格特根据任务控制中心指令打开二号罐风扇之举产生[[电弧|电弧]]，导致氧气瓶着火<ref name="Chaikin-1998" />{{rp|333}}。

委员会还用装有点火线路的氧气瓶测试，罐内温度急剧升高并爆炸，情况与阿波罗13号服务舱二号罐类似<ref name="Accident report, appendix F–H">{{cite book | title = Report of Apollo 13 Review Board, appendix F–H | url = https://history.nasa.gov/afj/ap13fj/pdf/a13-review-report-app-f-g-h-19700078913.pdf | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922061526/https://history.nasa.gov/afj/ap13fj/pdf/a13-review-report-app-f-g-h-19700078913.pdf | archive-date = 2020-09-22 | format = PDF | access-date = 2021-02-10}}</ref>{{rp|F-48–F-49}}。服务舱四号托架类似面板经过测试同样因爆炸与测试设备分离<ref name="Accident report, appendix F–H" />{{rp|F-70–F-82}}。

=== 对应变更 ===
[[File:Apollo_14_redesigned_oxygen_tank_(S71-16745).jpg|thumb]]

从[[阿波罗14号|阿波罗14号]]开始，氧气瓶经过重新设计，温控器升级后能应对适当电压，加热器是维持氧气压力所需，所以必须保留。罐内不再安装电动马达不密封的搅拌风扇，这也意味着氧气存量表读数不一定准确，同时增加第三个氧气瓶，确保每个罐存氧不至低于一半。<ref name="Gatland-1976">{{cite book | last = Gatland | first = Kenneth | title = Manned Spacecraft | url = https://archive.org/details/mannedspacecraft0000gatl | publisher = MacMillan | edition = Second | year = 1976 | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-02-542820-1 | page = [https://archive.org/details/mannedspacecraft0000gatl/page/281 281]}}</ref>三号罐装在服务舱一号托架，与另外两个罐相对，还配有能把燃料电池和另外两个罐隔断、只向指令舱供氧的隔离阀。各储罐内的存量探测器由铝制升级成不锈钢。<ref name="Apollo 14 Press Kit-1971">{{cite book | title = Apollo 14 Press Kit | publisher = NASA | location = Washington, D.C. | year = 1971 | url = https://www.nasa.gov/specials/apollo50th/pdf/A14_PressKit.pdf | id = 71-3K | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210108204942/https://www.nasa.gov/specials/apollo50th/pdf/A14_PressKit.pdf | format = PDF | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-date = 2021-01-08}}</ref>{{rp|96–97}}

四号托架所有电线采用不锈钢护套。燃料电池供氧阀重新设计，将[[聚四氟乙烯|聚四氟乙烯]]涂层的布线与氧气隔离。航天器与任务控制中心的监控系统修改后能更及时并显眼地发出异常情况警告。<ref name="Gatland-1976" />指令舱加装19升应急用水，服务舱增加与登月舱下降段供电电池相同的应急电池。登月舱也经修改，能更方便地向指令舱输送电能。<ref name="Apollo 14 Press Kit-1971" />{{rp|96–98}}此外，[[S-II|二级火箭]]还增加设备抵消纵向耦合振动<ref name="Apollo 14 Press Kit-1971" />{{rp|95}}。

== 余波和影响 ==
[[File:President_Richard_Nixon_speaks_before_awarding_the_Apollo_13_astronauts_the_Presidential_Medal_of_Freedom.jpg|thumb]]总统向阿波罗13号宇航员颁授[[總統自由勳章|總統自由勳章]]]]

1971年2月5日，[[阿波罗14号|阿波罗14号]]登月舱“安塔瑞斯”带着宇航员[[艾伦·谢泼德|艾伦·谢泼德]]与[[艾德加·米切尔|艾德加·米切尔]]在弗拉·毛罗高地附近降落，实现阿波罗13号未竟的探索目标<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.lpi.usra.edu/lunar/missions/apollo/apollo_14/landing_site/ | title = Apollo 14 mission: Landing site | accessdate = 2020-10-31 | publisher = [[月球與行星研究所|Lunar and Planetary Institute]] | website = USRA | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170617184232/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/lunar/missions/apollo/apollo_14/landing_site/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2017-06-17}}</ref>。海斯在安塔瑞斯下降期间担任航天器通讯员<ref>{{cite web | url = https://history.nasa.gov/alsj/a14/a14.landing.html | title = Landing at Far Mauro | editor-last = Jones | editor-first = Eric M. | work = Apollo 14 Lunar Surface Journal | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811110059/https://history.nasa.gov/alsj/a14/a14.landing.html | publisher = NASA | access-date = 2021-02-10 | date = 2016-01-12 | archive-date = 2020-08-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，还在谢泼德与米切尔第二次月表舱外活动、探索圆锥环形山附近时担任通讯员<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811095710/https://history.nasa.gov/alsj/a14/a14.tocone.html | archive-date = 2020-08-11 | url = https://history.nasa.gov/alsj/a14/a14.tocone.html | title = Climbing Cone Ridge – where are we? | editor-last = Jones | editor-first = Eric M. | work = Apollo 14 Lunar Surface Journal | publisher = NASA | access-date = 2021-02-10 | date = 2017-09-29}}</ref>。

阿波罗13号的宇航员再也没有飞上太空。洛弗尔1973年从航空航天局退休并从海军退役，此后在私营企业工作<ref name="nasabio">{{cite web | url = https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/atoms/files/lovell_james_0.pdf | title = Astronaut Bio: James A. Lovell | access-date = 2021-02-10 | publisher = NASA | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200916072920/https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/atoms/files/lovell_james_0.pdf | archive-date = 2020-09-16 | format = PDF}}</ref>。斯威格特原计划参加1975年[[阿波罗-联盟测试计划|阿波罗-联盟测试计划]]，但因[[阿波罗15号邮封丑闻|阿波罗15号邮封丑闻]]影响被迫退出。1973年他在航空航天局休假后离开并走上从政道路，1982年当选联邦众议员，但未及宣誓就职便死于癌症。<ref>{{cite web | title = For Jack Swigert, on his 83rd birthday | last = Carney | first = Emily | url = https://www.americaspace.com/2014/08/29/for-jack-swigert-on-his-83rd-birthday/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014225/https://www.americaspace.com/2014/08/29/for-jack-swigert-on-his-83rd-birthday/ | publisher = AmericaSpace | date = 2014-08-29 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref>海斯本是阿波罗19号指令长，该任务后来取消，他曾驾驶[[航天飞机|航天飞机]]执行[[进近与着陆测试|进近与着陆测试]]，后于1979年从航空航天局退休<ref>{{Cite web | first1 = Elizabeth | last1 = Howell | last2 = Hickok | first2 = Kimberly | title = Astronaut Fred Haise: Apollo 13 Crewmember | date = 2020-04-10 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | url = https://www.space.com/20318-fred-haise-apollo-13-biography.html | website = Space.com | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201223194405/https://www.space.com/20318-fred-haise-apollo-13-biography.html | publisher = Future US | archive-date = 2020-12-23}}</ref>。

阿波罗13号没有登上月球，但仍完成几项实验<ref name="13 science">{{cite web | title = Apollo 13 mission: Science experiments | website = Universities Space Research Association | publisher = Lunar and Planetary Institute | url = https://www.lpi.usra.edu/lunar/missions/apollo/apollo_13/experiments/ | access-date = 2018-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180915105402/https://www.lpi.usra.edu/lunar/missions/apollo/apollo_13/experiments/ | archive-date = 2018-09-15 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。过去的阿波罗任务发射火箭[[S-IVB|第三级]]与航天器分离后就会前往太阳轨道，阿波罗12号留在月表的地震仪探测到众多小物体撞击月球，但大型物体撞击能获得更多月球地壳信息，所以航空航天局决定从阿波罗13号开始用第三级火箭撞击月球<ref name="Harland-1999" />{{rp|50}}。撞击时间是任务开始后77小时56分40秒，位置距地震仪117公里，产生的能量已足够仪器增益所需<ref name="Orloff-Harland-2006" />{{rp|367}}。阿波罗12号遭遇雷击后，航空航天局决定增加实验，测量航天器上升到轨道期间大气中的电现象，阿波罗13号所获数据表明恶劣天气时的风险更高。阿波罗13号还拍下许多地球照片，用于测试[[地球同步卫星|同步卫星]]是否能判断云层高度，实验取得预期成果。<ref name="13 science" />

登月舱制造商格鲁门公司向服务与指令舱主承包商北美罗克韦尔发去搞笑账单，要求对方支付（登月舱）一路把服务与指令舱“拖”往月球再又“拖”回来的费用。项目包括第一英里起步价四美元，之后40万零1公里每公里加收一美元，电池、氧气收费536.05美元，另有四晚“其他客人入住”（指斯威格特，登月舱本来只容纳两人登月）的房费。去除两成“商业折扣”和两个百分点的及时付款折扣，账单总额为31万2421.24美元。北美罗克韦尔声称过去三次阿波罗任务都是服务与指令舱把登月舱运到月球，但一直没向格鲁门公司收费，故拒绝支付。<ref>{{cite web | website = Spaceflight Insider | access-date = 2021-02-10 | date = 2013-12-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041957/https://www.spaceflightinsider.com/space-centers/kennedy-space-center/the-apollo-13-invoice/ | title = The Apollo 13 Invoice... | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.spaceflightinsider.com/space-centers/kennedy-space-center/the-apollo-13-invoice/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Tongue-in-Cheek-Bill Asks Space Tow Fee | page = 7 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | date = 1970-04-18 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1338&dat=19700418&id=Owg0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=O_gDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5822,839543 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | archive-date = 2021-05-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210503044832/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1338&dat=19700418&id=Owg0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=O_gDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5822%2C839543 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1970-04-18 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | title = 'Towing' Fee Is Asked by Grumman | page = 13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200821122253/https://www.nytimes.com/1970/04/18/archives/towing-fee-is-asked-by-grumman.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1970/04/18/archives/towing-fee-is-asked-by-grumman.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-21}}</ref>
