指令舱拆解成零件后测试并保存多年，有些用在[[天空实验室救援|天空实验室救援任务]]的训练仪上，训练仪随后放在[[路易维尔科学中心|肯塔基科学中心]]展览。[[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]][[哈坎森_(堪萨斯州)|哈坎森]][[宇宙仪博物馆|宇宙仪博物馆]]的马克斯·阿里制订复原阿波罗指令舱的计划，如今“奥德赛”号便在博物馆展出。<ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2020-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200815082026/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35462879/apollo-13-capsule-headed-for-kansas/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35462879/apollo-13-capsule-headed-for-kansas/ | title = Apollo 13 Capsule Headed for Kansas | agency = Associated Press | date = 1996-12-29 | page = A2 | via = Newspapers.com | location = Manhattan, Kansas | newspaper = The Manhattan Mercury | dead-url = no}}</ref>

洛弗尔将阿波罗13号称为“成功的失败”<ref name="Cortright-1975" />{{rp|247–249}}。航天飞机宇航员[[邁克爾·馬西莫諾|邁克爾·馬西莫諾]]表示，阿波罗13号“展示国家航空航天局真正的凝聚力所在：团体协作、友谊互助”<ref name="Yahoo 50th" />。众多传媒将此次事故称为“国家航空航天局最伟大的时刻”并持续至今<ref name="Walt Disney's Honorary Oscars">{{cite web | first = Kim | last = Shiflett | access-date = 2021-02-10 | publisher = NASA | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125150106/https://www.nasa.gov/content/members-of-apollo-13-team-reflect-on-nasas-finest-hour/ | url = https://www.nasa.gov/content/members-of-apollo-13-team-reflect-on-nasas-finest-hour/ | title = Members of Apollo 13 Team Reflect on 'NASA's Finest Hour' | date = 2015-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | editor-last1 = Foerman | editor-first1 = Paul | editor-last2 = Thompson | editor-first2 = Lacy | date = 2010-04 | title = Apollo 13 – NASA's 'successful failure' | journal = Lagniappe | volume = 5 | issue = 4 | pages = 5–7 | location = Hancock County, Mississippi | publisher = [[斯坦尼斯航天中心|John C. Stennis Space Center]] | url = https://www.nasa.gov/centers/stennis/pdf/445767main_April_10_Lagniappe.pdf | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200928070705/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/stennis/pdf/445767main_April_10_Lagniappe.pdf | archive-date = 2020-09-28 | format = PDF | access-date = 2021-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.cgpublishing.com/Rpdf/Apollo%20EECOM%20Boeing%20News%201(FL)1.pdf | title = NASA's Finest Hour: Sy Liebergot recalls the race to save Apollo 13 | last = Seil | first = Bill | date = 2005-07-05 | work = Boeing News Now | publisher = [[波音|Boeing Company]] | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-07-26 | format = PDF | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726071430/http://www.cgpublishing.com/Rpdf/Apollo%20EECOM%20Boeing%20News%201(FL)1.pdf}}</ref><ref name="Chaikin-1998" />{{rp|335}}<ref name="Yahoo 50th" />。作家科林·伯吉斯写道：“阿波罗13号的飞行九死一生，极其戏剧化地证明载人航天固有风险极大。宇航员安全返回地球后，公众再度变得漠不关心。”<ref name="Burgess-2019">{{cite book | last = Burgess | first = Colin | year = 2019 | title = Shattered Dreams: The Lost and Canceled Space Missions | publisher = University of Nebraska Press | location = Lincoln, Nebraska | isbn = 978-1-4962-1422-5 | edition = eBook}}</ref>{{rp|23}}

威廉·康普顿的阿波罗计划主题著作指出，阿波罗13号“完全是凭借任务控制人员及时的英勇努力和临场发挥挽救乘组”<ref>{{cite book | last = Compton | first = William David | title = Where No Man has Gone Before: A History of Apollo Lunar Exploration Missions | series = NASA History Series | publisher = NASA | id = SP-4214 | year = 1989 | location = Washington, D.C. | oclc = 1045558568 | pages = 196–199}}</ref>。里克·休斯顿与[[米尔特·赫夫林|米尔特·赫夫林]]的任务控制中心历史著作表示：“阿波罗13号证明任务控制中心有能力把面临生命危险的太空旅行者带回家”<ref name="Houston-Heflin-Aaron-2015" />{{rp|199}}。前航空航天局首席历史学家[[罗杰·劳尼尤斯|罗杰·劳尼尤斯]]也称，阿波罗13号事故“巩固全世界对美国国家航空航天局能力的信心”，程度远超“航天飞行史上其他任何事故”<ref name="Launius-2019" />。不过，事故也促使载人航天中心主任吉鲁斯等官员认为，航空航天局如果继续执行阿波罗载人任务，迟早会有宇航员死于非命，要求尽快结束阿波罗计划<ref name="Launius-2019" />。尼克松的顾问建议取消剩余登月任务，声称一旦发生太空灾难，总统的政治资本将受重创<ref name="Chaikin-1998" />{{rp|336}}。国会削减预算，令总统更倾向于取消任务，阿波罗13号之后的暂停期里就有两项取消，阿波罗计划随1972年12月的[[阿波罗17号|阿波罗17号]]一起成为历史<ref name="Launius-2019" /><ref name="Burgess-2019" />{{rp|22–27}}。

