1974年的[[电视电影|电视电影]]《[[休斯顿，我们遇上麻烦|休斯顿，我们遇上麻烦]]》围绕阿波罗13号事故展开，但内容基本虚构，主要讲述紧急情况发生后地面人员面临的危机，如扰乱工作计划、生活压力进一步加大等。洛弗尔公开批评该片“纯属捏造、品味低劣”。<ref name="irks">{{cite news | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923141753/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088956/apollo-13-movie-irks-lovell-page-5/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088956/apollo-13-movie-irks-lovell-page-5/ | title = Apollo 13 Movie Irks Lovell | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The South Bend Tribune | location = South Bend, Indiana | date = 1974-02-28 | page = 5 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2020-11-28 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/retropolis/wp/2017/04/13/houston-we-have-a-problem-the-amazing-history-of-the-iconic-apollo-13-misquote/ | title = 'Houston, we have a problem': The amazing history of the iconic Apollo 13 misquote | newspaper = The Washington Post | date = 2017-04-13 | last = Rosenwald | first = Michael S. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128091343/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/retropolis/wp/2017/04/13/houston-we-have-a-problem-the-amazing-history-of-the-iconic-apollo-13-misquote/}}</ref>

1978年3月，[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]纪录电视剧《危在旦夕》播出《休斯顿……我们遇上麻烦》，除存在简化外基本准确地重现事故过程<ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2020-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200814202346/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35940813/the-week-in-view-page-29/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35940813/the-week-in-view-page-29/ | title = The Week in View | last = Meades | first = Jonathan | newspaper = The Observer | location = London, England | date = 1978-03-26 | page = 29 | dead-url = no | via = Newspapers.com}}</ref>。1994年，[[公共广播电视公司|公共广播电视公司]]在[[阿波罗11号周年庆|阿波罗11号25周年]]期间播出90分钟纪录片《阿波罗13号：生死边缘》<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35947551/wednesday-highlights-page-25/ | title = Wednesday Highlights | department = TV Week | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | location = Chicago, Illinois | date = 1994-07-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200814204420/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35947551/wednesday-highlights-page-25/ | page = 25 | via = Newspapers.com | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-date = 2020-08-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35947573/space-specials-at-a-glance-page-3/ | title = Space Specials at a Glance | newspaper = Florida Today | department = TV Week | location = Cocoa, Florida | date = 1994-07-17 | page = 3 | via = Newspapers.com | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-date = 2020-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130120114/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35947573/space-specials-at-a-glance-page-3/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

三名宇航员原计划合作著书，但尚未开始便相继离开航空航天局。洛弗尔1991年退休后，新闻工作者[[傑弗里·克魯格|傑弗里·克魯格]]主动与他联系，计划创作记载阿波罗13号任务的纪实著作。斯威格特已在1982年辞世，海斯此时不再对写书感兴趣。1994年，洛弗尔与克鲁格合著的《与月球失之交臂》出版。<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/39589313/the-post-crescent-11-december-1994/ | title = Lovell Describes the Dark Side of Moon Shots | newspaper = The Post-Crescent | location = Appleton, Wisconsin | agency = Associated Press | last = Dunn | first = Marcia | date = 1994-12-11 | page = F-8 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818081339/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/39589313/the-post-crescent-11-december-1994/ | archive-date = 2020-08-18 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

《与月球失之交臂》一年后改编成电影《[[阿波罗13号_(电影)|阿波罗13号]]》（1995年），[[朗·侯活|朗·侯活]]执导，汤姆·汉克斯扮演洛弗尔，[[比爾·派斯頓|比爾·派斯頓]]饰海斯，[[凯文·贝肯|凯文·贝肯]]出演斯威格特，[[蓋瑞·辛尼茲|蓋瑞·辛尼茲]]诠释马丁利，[[艾德·哈里斯|艾德·哈里斯]]扮演克兰兹，[[凯瑟琳·奎南|凯瑟琳·奎南]]饰演玛丽莲。洛弗尔与克兰兹等亲历者表示，出于戏剧效果考虑片中难免会有艺术处理，但仍然相当真实地再现任务经过。例如洛弗尔跟在斯威格特原话后面的名言“休斯顿，我们遇上麻烦”在片中采用不同时态。<ref name="journal Houston" /><ref name = "nasaMembers" />哈里斯扮演克兰兹时所说台词“[[绝对不能失败|绝对不能失败]]”纯属电影创作，但对克兰兹本人影响很大，2000年他的自传便以这句短语为题<ref name="nasaMembers">{{Cite web | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125150106/https://www.nasa.gov/content/members-of-apollo-13-team-reflect-on-nasas-finest-hour/ | url = https://www.nasa.gov/content/members-of-apollo-13-team-reflect-on-nasas-finest-hour/ | title = Members of Apollo 13 Team Reflect on 'NASA's Finest Hour' | last = Granath | first = Bob | date = 2015-04-17 | publisher = NASA}}</ref>。《阿波罗13号》获九项[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]提名，最后赢得[[奥斯卡最佳剪辑奖|最佳剪辑]]和[[奥斯卡最佳音效奖|音效]]两项大奖<ref>{{cite news | via = Newspapers.com | page = 4B | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728091847/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088898/the-winners-page-4b/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088898/the-winners-page-4b/ | title = The Winners | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Herald-Palladium | location = Saint Joseph, Michigan | date = 1996-03-26 | archive-date = 2020-07-28 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2020-08-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200804002058/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088927/braveheart-apollo-13-lead-oscar/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35088927/braveheart-apollo-13-lead-oscar/ | title = 'Braveheart', 'Apollo 13' Lead Oscar Nominees | newspaper = St. Louis Post Dispatch | location = St. Louis, Missouri | date = 1996-02-14 | page = 4A | via = Newspapers.com | last = Barnes | first = Harper}}</ref>。

1998年电视短剧《[[从地球到月球_(电视短剧)|从地球到月球]]》由汉克斯和霍华德共同担任制作人，分集《我们中断节目》讲述阿波罗13号经历。短剧没有再像三年前的电影那样从乘组角度讲述任务经过，而是从地球视角展示电视记者争相报导事故。<ref>{{cite news | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200814210127/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35053645/tom-hanks-flies-us-to-the-moon-via/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/35053645/tom-hanks-flies-us-to-the-moon-via/ | title = Tom Hanks Flies us to the Moon via HBO | newspaper = Santa Cruz Sentinel | location = Santa Cruz, California | date = 1998-04-05 | page = C- 6 | agency = The New York Times | via = Newspapers.com | last = Sterngold | first = James | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-14 | access-date = 2021-02-10}}</ref>

2020年，[[英國廣播公司國際頻道|英國廣播公司國際頻道]]开始播出广播节目《登月13分钟》，其中采用航空航天局的阿波罗任务音频、档案以及最近对涉事人员的访谈。第二季从2020年3月8日开始播映，第一集便是《定时炸弹：阿波罗13号 》，从火箭发射讲到爆炸。第二集详细介绍任务控制中心对事故的否认与怀疑，后面的分集关注任务其他方面。受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，最后一集（第七集）延迟播出，英国广播公司宣称节目主持人[[凯文·方|凯文·方]]是医生，需要行使济世救人的职责。<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w13xttx2/episodes/downloads | title = 13 minutes to the moon, season 2 | work = BBC podcast | access-date = 2021-02-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210129230544/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w13xttx2/episodes/downloads | archive-date = 2021-01-29}}</ref>

2020年是阿波罗13号任务50周年，交互式多媒体网站[[实时阿波罗|实时阿波罗]]上线，用户能跟随任务过程查看照片和视频，聆听休斯顿和宇航员的对话，以及任务控制人员之间的交流<ref>{{cite journal | title = Relive the drama of Apollo 13 in real time, as it happened | date = 2020-04-08 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | last = Reichhardt | first = Tony | publisher = Smithsonian Institution | journal = Air and Space Magazine | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018060928/https://www.airspacemag.com/daily-planet/relive-drama-apollo-13-real-time-it-happened-180974625/ | archive-date = 2020-10-18 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.airspacemag.com/daily-planet/relive-drama-apollo-13-real-time-it-happened-180974625/}}</ref>。受冠状病毒病疫情影响，50周年期间（2020年4月）航空航天局没有举办现场活动，但在4月10日首映新纪录片《阿波罗13号：安全回家》<ref>{{cite web | title = Celebrate Apollo 13 at 50 with NASA's 'Home Safe' documentary (and much more!) | last = Howell | first = Elizabeth | publisher = space.com | url = https://www.space.com/apollo-13-50th-anniversary-webcast-digital-celebrations.html | date = 2020-04-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021074038/https://www.space.com/apollo-13-50th-anniversary-webcast-digital-celebrations.html | access-date = 2021-02-10 | archive-date = 2020-10-21 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，此外还有众多活动推迟<ref>{{cite web | title = Houston, we've had a delay: Apollo 13 50th celebrations rescheduled | last = Pearlman | first = Robert Z. | url = https://www.space.com/apollo13-50th-celebrations-rescheduled.html | date = 2020-04-09 | access-date = 2021-02-10 | publisher = space.com | archive-date = 2020-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201212121629/https://www.space.com/apollo13-50th-celebrations-rescheduled.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

